title: WTB:  Just one, Bender w/ Trees!
author: ZiggerZagger

posts.post_title: WTB:  Just one, Bender w/ Trees!
posts.post_content:
Hi all,

Finished the long road to 520 on the T206 set in late 2020.  Was a ton of fun, with lots of great board members helping out.

Finally got a PSA submission back with the other 5 remaining cards, after 7 months away on a 20-day submission...  I think a lot of us are in the same boat here.   
That leaves my only non-PSA graded card in the 520 as this particular Bender.

I am in need of one PSA-graded copy, a Bender w/ Trees in PSA 4.0 - 6.0.  
A copy in a '5' would be absolutely ideal, but any help at all is appreciated.

Have PP Gift funds at the ready.  If a trade or part-exchange is preferred I do have a centered SGC 4 Bender w/ Trees.
Also have some other nice stuff back -- PSA 4 George Mullin (throwing) and Wildfire Schulte (Front View), both are tough, and an SGC 4 Bud Sharpe as well.

Thanks in advance!
|
